text: Yukiyasu Ishikawa (born 9 May 1965) is a Japanese rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Japan Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
